replies.body:
Hey man, I sent a Riot Support ticket about my own problem, not sure if you’re getting it as well but, for me on my main account:

I press ‘Play’ and it makes me wait 20 minutes. I wait out the 20 minutes and as soon as the window closes, the 20 minutes loops back and another window pops up and makes me wait another 20 minutes. This has happened 3 times in a row now including two days ago, and the Rioters said that they are aware that this ‘Penalty Wait Loop’ is happening and affecting quite a few players (but not the majority in Low Priority Queue).

